Our Mission Statement

Our Goal at Sproutr is to create habits that matter most to people and be able to track them. We want to show how these habits can really impact our lives and make us more engaged in our day to day. Our mission is to empower every person and every organization on the planet to achieve more. It is no different than planting a seed and tending to it, habits need to be watered and monitored. You will see the progress made and appreciate watching the habits you set in place grow and become natural.

hab·it

noun

1. A habit is a routine of behavior that is repeated regularly and tends to occur subconsciously. The American Journal of Psychology defined a "habit, from the standpoint of psychology, [as] a more or less fixed way of thinking, willing, or feeling acquired through previous repetition of a mental experience."
